{"tid":581681,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇師兄係spca領養過成貓？？","createTime":"2018-03-05T14:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T03:02:26.000Z","uid":136039,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"99aa9a1be55a8e6c07a49407d3dc226b58b67b10","tid":581681,"uid":136039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:14:52.000Z","msg":"想係愛護動物協會領養喵喵，因為好驚幼貓好難湊，自己又冇咩經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以想領養成貓<br />\n有冇過來人可以分享下？領養要求高唔高？<br />\n去睇中岩既，然後先裝窗網，買籠，得唔得？定係要預先裝網買籠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n麻煩各路師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24bff12d839b72065bd6dade368c268acc1bb51b","tid":581681,"uid":136039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:16:21.000Z","msg":"順帶一問，仲讀緊書有冇機會領養到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36985056cc11ac6cb1b3a87df36087a825bbe16","tid":581681,"uid":136039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:59:56.000Z","msg":"U"},{"pid":"f175ab06cf0846a3e1f58172c2b6ee73fd9a0334","tid":581681,"uid":2431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"99aa9a1be55a8e6c07a49407d3dc226b58b67b10","tid":581681,"uid":136039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:14:52.000Z","msg":"想係愛護動物協會領養喵喵，因為好驚幼貓好難湊，自己又冇咩經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以想領養成貓<br />\n有冇過來人可以分享下？領養要求高唔高？<br />\n去睇中岩既，然後先裝窗網，買籠，得唔得？定係要預先裝網買籠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n麻煩各路師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T03:11:25.000Z","msg":"我係喺spca領養，不過係幼貓<br />\n唔介意嘅我都分享吓<br />\n<br />\n上spca個網見到大多數都寫住hold，即係代表已經有申請人睇中隻貓貓，排緊隊等approve<br />\n不過去到愛協領養中心，staff都建議我填咗申請表先，未必寫咗hold就代表無機<br />\n<br />\n而我嗰陣係裝哂窗網先去睇貓貓，填表嘅時候show埋窗網嘅相俾staff睇<br />\n<br />\n最後填完表後嘅兩個鐘就打電話嚟話可以接走貓貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，咁我就臨時問朋友借籠，不過領養中心好似都有得賣<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>順帶一問，仲讀緊書有冇機會領養到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果搵你屋企人同你一齊去申請，個機會應該大過一個學生自己去申請？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲staff應該都係想睇你地屋企係咪有能力負擔，會唔會有時間陪吓貓貓<br />\n利申 一家人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9edaf34da92380957f657d51f7f0431029a70a1","tid":581681,"uid":75307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T07:29:52.000Z","msg":"SPCA呢排好少貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ee6bfac2d9fc3805b8a03373cd47cff8633928","tid":581681,"uid":67151,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T07:32:49.000Z","msg":"同女朋友一齊去領養，send 左啲窗網相比佢就批左。<br />\n兩個都讀緊書，不過我自己住，屋企人長期唔喺到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99a008a4aa290ad4094a3038551468c612b9011","tid":581681,"uid":45118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T07:37:00.000Z","msg":"你上佢地個網睇或直接去佢地中心睇貓，玩一陣睇下夾唔夾，填表，等電話，等電話期間可以整定窗網，到時俾相佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定無義工咁麻撚煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b964f6962b7368de9e47f3f40ae99110716efa2e","tid":581681,"uid":136039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f175ab06cf0846a3e1f58172c2b6ee73fd9a0334","tid":581681,"uid":2431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"99aa9a1be55a8e6c07a49407d3dc226b58b67b10","tid":581681,"uid":136039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:14:52.000Z","m